{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"BIPV Energy Yield API","description":"\n## BIPV Energy Yield & Financial Analysis API\nResearch-grade implementation — every model traces directly to a named,\npeer-reviewed publication. No black boxes, no undocumented assumptions.\n### Academic & Standards Basis\n| Model | Source |\n|---|---|\n| Irradiance transposition | Reindl, Beckman & Duffie (1990) Solar Energy 45(5) |\n| Diffuse fraction | Erbs, Klein & Duffie (1982) Solar Energy 28(4) |\n| Cell temperature | Ross (1976) · King et al. SAND2004-3535 |\n| BIPV temp validation | Martín-Chivelet et al. (2022) Sustainability 14(3):1500 |\n| BIPV integration losses | IEA PVPS Task 15 (2018) |\n| Yield & PR | IEC 61724-1:2021 · EN 50583-2:2016 |\n| LCOE methodology | IRENA (2023) Renewable Power Generation Costs |\n| Degradation | Jordan & Kurtz (2013) Progress in Photovoltaics 21(1) |\n| CO₂ intensity | IEA (2023) CO₂ Emissions from Fuel Combustion |\n### Plans\n**Free** (10 calls) · **Pro** $49/mo · **Enterprise** $199/mo\n","version":"2.0.0"},"paths":{"/":{"get":{"tags":["Info"],"summary":"Root","operationId":"root__get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/health":{"get":{"tags":["Info"],"summary":"Health","operationId":"health_health_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/irradiance":{"get":{"tags":["Data"],"summary":"Get Irradiance Data","description":"NASA POWER irradiance data for any location. Pro/Enterprise plan required.","operationId":"get_irradiance_data_irradiance_get","security":[{"APIKeyHeader":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"latitude","in":"query","required":true,"schema":{"type":"number","maximum":90.0,"minimum":-90.0,"title":"Latitude"}},{"name":"longitude","in":"query","required":true,"schema":{"type":"number","maximum":180.0,"minimum":-180.0,"title":"Longitude"}},{"name":"x-rapidapi-proxy-secret","in":"header","required":fa